# server-setup TODO

Goal: flake with reusable `nixosModules.base` and per-host configs under `hosts/<name>/`, deployable across a growing fleet via deploy-rs. k3s, tailscale, and other orchestration come **after** the multi-host config workflow is solid.

## Decisions (locked in)

| Topic | Decision |
|-------|----------|
| Fleet | omen01 is the first host; more machines will follow |
| Users | `users.users.caden` in `base.nix` â€” shared across all hosts |
| SSH keys | Same authorized keys on every host (in `base.nix`) |
| Hostname | `omen01` |
| Channel | `nixos-unstable` |
| v1 scope | `base` module + `omen01` host only (no k3s/tailscale yet) |
| Deploy | deploy-rs (remote rebuild/switch from this repo) |
| Orchestration | Deferred until fleet config management is working |

